  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then they got there was born a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I hear-- I don't know exactly-- when they take them out to Auschwitz, she tore out the child, the girl, the baby, and they hand to a Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I don't know which station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I don't know the name of the woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So it's like you take-- you drop something in [? a river of water, ?] you cannot find.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "From Fela with me and Yehuda was receive a letter 1946 from my cousins from Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He comes back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he tells me, listen, this is a letter from your sister, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Anja ?] and Fela.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She wrote to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There were no-- no surviving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The youngest sister, Cela, she was writing, writing also to the same cousin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] this letter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I lost.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Maybe my wife put it away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Then I never see the letter, because every time when I saw the letter, it struck me on the heart.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[CRYING] She wrote, I am 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I like so the life, but if to die, she [? not ?] and I am with, with the gun, at least on the road like my brother, not like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Maybe she put it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "With the years, now she cannot find this letter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And this is the life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I am sitting here remembering, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "If people will came and will tell, never was a Holocaust, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] maybe they will tell that Stalingrad was only a play.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "If they can tell that, they can tell this also was never in the history of mankind was a fight like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But I hope man can learn.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
